uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model

Class MFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.CValue<CFrame>
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.MFrame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEntity, MEntity

    public class MFrame
extends CValue<CFrame>
implements MEntity
    Represents a meta-level model-entity that defines a set of concept-level frames via a root concept-level frame.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Concrete Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean constrained()
      Stipulates that this meta-level frame does define specific constraints on the concept-level frames that it defines (the constraints being that the concept-level frames must be concept-level frames subsumed by the root concept-level frame).
      boolean equals(java.lang.Object other)
      Tests for equality between this and other specified object, which will hold if and only if the other object is another MFrame with the same root concept-level frame as this one, as determined via the relevant equals method.
      java.lang.String getDisplayLabel()
      Provides a label for the entity, suitable for displaying to an end-user.
      CFrame getRootCFrame()
      Provides the root concept-level frame.
      java.lang.Class<CFrame> getValueType()
      Specifies the class of the value-entities defined by this value-type-entity.
      int hashCode()
      Provides hash-code based on hash-code of root concept-level frame.
      boolean onePossibleValue()
      Stipulates that this meta-level frame defines only a single possible value if and only if it's root concept-level frame has no sub-frames with visibility status of CVisibility.EXPOSED.
      boolean subsumes(CValue<?> other)
      Tests whether this value-type-entity subsumes another specified value-type-entity, which will be the case if and only if the other value-type-entity is another MFrame object whose root concept-level frame is subsumed by the root concept-level frame of this one, as determined via the CFrame.subsumes(CFrame) method.
      java.lang.String toString()
      Provides a description of the entity, intended to provide information to the software developer, and not suitable for displaying to an end-user.
      MFrame toUnconstrained()
      Provides the unconstrained version of this meta-level frame, which will be the root meta-level frame.
